Template: war1gus/extractdata
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: (from the CD, Floppy version, or a local install).
 You must now extract the Warcraft data files

Template: war1gus/cdpath
Type: string
Default: /media/cdrom
Description: Warcraft: Orcs & Humans CD mount point:
 Enter path to your Warcraft: Orcs & Humans CD mount point

Template: war1gus/extractvideo
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Extract and convert videos?
 Only the Warcraft CD version contains videos. Extracting and
 converting may take a couple of minutes.

Template: war1gus/convertmusic
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Convert MIDI music to ogg?
 Warcraft music is in MIDI format. Converting will take a
 few minutes.

Template: war1gus/nodata
Type: error
Description: Data files not found
 Warcraft was not found in the specified path. Specify another
 path which contains correct Warcraft data files.
